<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>{{title}}</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <div>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvvirefzi/image/upload/v1743526776/klarify-logo_v2yhrm.png"
          alt="Logo"
          class="logo"
          style="max-width: 120px;"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        style="padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #eee; color: #1e1c1c;"
      >
        <div
          style="padding: 5px; text-align: center; font-weight: 500; font-size: 24px; color: #000000;"
        >
          Reset your Password
        </div>
        <p>{{greeting}}</p>
        <p>We heard that you lost your Klarify password. Sorry about that!</p>
        <p>But don’t worry! You can use the following button to reset your
          password:</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <a
            href="{{buttonUrl}}"
            style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: semiBold; color: white; background-color: #0f084e; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;"
          >{{buttonText}}</a>
        </div>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this
          email. Your password will not be changed.</p>
        <p>This link will expire in 1 hours for security reasons.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />Klarify Team</p>
      </div>
      <div
        style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #888; font-size: 0.8em;"
      >
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>© {{year}} Klarify. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>